data.description: Beautiful updated home situated on a .51 lot in Porter Hills off Bear Creek Pike!. Easy access to I-65 and Saturn Parkway, downtown Columbia, schools, shopping, and restaurants. No HOA fees, quite street, all kitchen appliances stay including SS fridge w/middle drawer, also has built-in wall oven. This ranch style brick home has a newly painted exterior/interior, new flooring and new gutters, offering 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms. It has a formal living room, dining room, large family room with eat in kitchen area, and a galley style kitchen. Downstairs has a full unfinished basement with lots of room for your projects, which can be easily finished and still have room to park 2 cars. It has a large back yard that has great opportunity and a great spot for shed or park trailer.
